---
// Problema.astro - The problem we solve section with 3 glass cards
---

<section class="section problema reveal" id="servicios" aria-label="The problem we solve">
  <h2 class="section-title">A business not on the internet,<br><span class="text-terracota">doesn't exist</span>.</h2>
  <div class="problema-grid">
    <div class="glass-card problema-card tall">
      <h4>They can't find you</h4>
      <p>When someone searches for what you sell, your competitor shows up. <strong>You just lost a customer you never knew existed.</strong></p>
      <p class="sub">No website = invisible. Not showing up on Google = invisible. If they can't find you, they can't buy you.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="glass-card problema-card">
      <h4>They don't trust you</h4>
      <p>A visitor judges your business in under 3 seconds. An outdated site, a slow loader, a broken layout — <strong>that's the last impression you get.</strong></p>
      <p class="sub">Design is trust. A $200 template screams "I don't care." Your customers notice.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="glass-card problema-card">
      <h4>They don't buy</h4>
      <p>Traffic without conversion is just a metric. If your site doesn't guide, persuade, and close — <strong>you're paying for visits that leave.</strong></p>
      <p class="sub">No clear CTA, no social proof, no urgency. A beautiful brochure that collects dust.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
